properties.name: Insurance Claim
properties.documentation:
Formal request by a policyholder or a counterparty to an insurance company for compensation for a covered damage, loss or other policy event.

The insurance company validates the claim and, once approved, provides compensation to the insured or an approved interested party on behalf of the insured.
